{"data":[{"date":"03:12 24/07","title":"Klopp t\u1ecf l\u00f2ng \"th\u01b0\u01a1ng h\u1ea1i\" Tottenham","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/9/klopp-to-long-thuong-hai-tottenham.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Th\u1ea5u hi\u1ec3u n\u1ed7i kh\u1ed1n kh\u00f3 c\u1ee7a Liverpool v\u1edbi t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh s\u1ee9t m\u1ebb l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i sau k\u1ef3 World Cup 2018, HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c c\u00e0ng th\u1ea5y c\u1ea3m th\u00f4ng cho Tottenham.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Liverpool \u0111ang tham gia v\u00e0o chuy\u1ebfn du \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00e8 tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t M\u1ef9 v\u1edbi n\u00f2ng c\u1ed1t ch\u1ee7 y\u1ebfu l\u00e0 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00f4n l\u00ean t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ed9i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb, khi c\u00e1c tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t v\u1eabn \u0111ang trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i sau k\u1ef3 World Cup 2018.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Th\u1eddi gian chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 kh\u00f4ng nhi\u1ec1u, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed nhi\u1ec1u ng\u00f4i sao \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc nguy c\u01a1 v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t ngay c\u1ea3 khi Premier League \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c kh\u1edfi tranh. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Klopp n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 Tottenham v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 th\u01b0\u01a1ng h\u1ea1i cho l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng s\u1ee9t m\u1ebb h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Klopp n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 Tottenham v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 th\u01b0\u01a1ng h\u1ea1i cho l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng s\u1ee9t m\u1ebb h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/9/klopp-to-long-thuong-hai-tottenham.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\u0110\u00f3ng g\u00f3p nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 nh\u1ea5t \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018, Tottenham hi\u1ec3n nhi\u00ean s\u1ee9t m\u1ebb l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Th\u1ea5u hi\u1ec3u n\u1ed7i kh\u1ed1n kh\u00f3 c\u1ee7a Liverpool v\u1edbi t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh s\u1ee9t m\u1ebb l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, HLV Jurgen Klopp c\u00e0ng th\u1ea5y c\u1ea3m th\u00f4ng cho Tottenham, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 nh\u1ea5t \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i v\u1edbi 9 ng\u01b0\u1eddi, hi\u1ec3n nhi\u00ean c\u0169ng \u0111ang ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ecbu thi\u1ec7t th\u00f2i nh\u1ea5t.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Qua \u0111\u00e2y, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c c\u0169ng k\u00eau g\u1ecdi c\u00e1c c\u01a1 quan \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00e0nh nh\u01b0 UEFA c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc l\u1ea1i vi\u1ec7c s\u1eafp x\u1ebfp l\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf sao cho h\u1ee3p l\u00fd v\u00e0 ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p h\u01a1n v\u1edbi th\u1ec3 tr\u1ea1ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 gi\u1edbi h\u1ea1n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7. HLV Klopp n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 Tottenham cho bi\u1ebft:<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cGi\u1edd th\u00ec ch\u00fang ta chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb c\u00f3 Nations League (gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u giao h\u1eefu c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9 \u0110TQG nh\u01b0ng l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng t\u00ednh \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u00e2n h\u1ea1t gi\u1ed1ng cho c\u00e1c chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i), t\u1ee9c l\u00e0 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i l\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i ch\u1ec9 sau ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea7y hai th\u00e1ng sau World Cup.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cTh\u1eadt \u0111i\u00ean r\u1ed3, v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea5y l\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 4 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u01b0\u1edbng m\u1eafc nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0y. Tr\u00f4ng sang Tottenham v\u1edbi 9 ng\u01b0\u1eddi, t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng hi\u1ec3u h\u1ecd s\u1ebd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1eed tr\u00ed ra sao n\u1eefa. C\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 th\u00ec b\u1eaft bu\u1ed9c v\u1eabn ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/goc-nhin-vi-hien-tai-va-tuong-lai-tottenham-hay-vo-dich-world-cup-421-190976.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/11/goc-nhin-vi-hien-tai-va-tuong-lai-tottenham-hay-vo-dich-world-cup.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/goc-nhin-vi-hien-tai-va-tuong-lai-tottenham-hay-vo-dich-world-cup-421-190976.html\">G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn: V\u00ec hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i v\u00e0 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, Tottenham h\u00e3y v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup!</span><br>\r\nTottenham ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 CLB \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 nh\u1ea5t \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 v\u00e0 vi\u1ec5n c\u1ea3nh \u00edt nh\u1ea5t m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao Spurs n\u00e2ng cao c\u00fap v\u00e0ng \u0111ang hi\u1ec3n hi\u1ec7n r\u00f5 n\u00e9t, \u00e2u...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1556","checkdouble":"191867"},{"date":"00:36 24/07","title":"Deschamps c\u1ea1n l\u1eddi khi Kante xu\u1ed1ng phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1edf chung k\u1ebft World Cup","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/16/deschamps-can-loi-khi-kante-xuong-phong-do-o-chung-ket-world-cup.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>H\u1ebft l\u1eddi ng\u1ee3i khen N\u2019Golo Kante nh\u01b0ng HLV Didier Deschamps c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch n\u1ed5i m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ee9c c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 Chelsea trong tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p vs Croatia chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">D\u00f9 sao, m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng hi\u1ebfm hoi khi \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi Qu\u1ea3 B\u00f3ng V\u00e0ng Luka Modric \u0111\u00f3, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed s\u1edbm b\u1ecb thay ra khi th\u1eddi gian thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f2n ch\u01b0a \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u1ed9t gi\u1edd \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u1ed3, c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ebfn ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Kh\u00f4ng ai c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn t\u00e0i n\u0103ng v\u00e0 t\u1ea7m c\u1ee1 quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a N\u2019Golo Kante tr\u00ean h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u01b0a Les Bleus gi\u00e0nh c\u00fap v\u00e0ng th\u1ee9 hai trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed, tuy nhi\u00ean t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i \u00edt nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1eb7t d\u1ea5u h\u1ecfi th\u1eafc m\u1eafc cho phong \u0111\u1ed9 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd \u0111i xu\u1ed1ng c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao Chelsea thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi vai tr\u00f2 \u201cm\u00e1y qu\u00e9t\u201d \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Deschamps vs Kante tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p vs Croatia chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Deschamps vs Kante tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p vs Croatia chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/16/deschamps-can-loi-khi-kante-xuong-phong-do-o-chung-ket-world-cup.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Kante tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p vs Croatia chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 xu\u1ed1ng phong \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00ec \u0111au d\u1ea1 d\u00e0y</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ngay c\u1ea3 HLV Didier Deschamps c\u0169ng c\u1ea1n l\u1eddi gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch lu\u00f4n khi chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 c\u1eadu h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t: \u201cT\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft chuy\u1ec7n g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 x\u1ea3y ra v\u1edbi N\u2019Golo trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft nh\u01b0ng c\u00f3 v\u1ebb n\u00f3 th\u1eadt t\u1ec7 cho c\u1eadu \u1ea5y. D\u00f9 sao, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y v\u1eabn v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh m\u1ea5t ni\u1ec1m tin c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 v\u00ec m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u nh\u01b0 v\u1eady.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cKhi N\u2019Golo r\u1eddi s\u00e2n, t\u00f4i h\u1ecfi th\u0103m li\u1ec7u c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 \u1ed5n kh\u00f4ng. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y ch\u1ec9 tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1eebng lo cho m\u00ecnh, h\u00e3y c\u1ee9 t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft. N\u2019Golo l\u00e0 v\u1eady, m\u1ed9t tia n\u1eafng mang y\u00eau th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t hi\u1ec7n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng, m\u1ed9t ngu\u1ed3n c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p s\u1ef1 nh\u1ecf b\u00e9 khi\u00eam nh\u01b0\u1eddng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, Kante \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi c\u01a1n \u0111au d\u1ea1 d\u00e0y v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ch\u1ecbu n\u1ed5i th\u00eam \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u1eefa sau kho\u1ea3ng 10 ph\u00fat hi\u1ec7p hai. Th\u00eam v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3 b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh th\u1ec3 tr\u1ea1ng, c\u00f3 th\u00f4ng tin cho hay anh trai ng\u00f4i sao Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed9t t\u1eed ngay tr\u01b0\u1edbc ng\u00e0y di\u1ec5n ra tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft, \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng nhi\u00ean \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng t\u00e2m l\u00fd qu\u00e1 l\u1edbn n\u1ebfu \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00fang l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/qua-de-thuong-kante-ngo-tau-ngai-di-hoi-xin-nho-ban-muon-ho-cup-vang-de-song-ao-421-191369.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/16/qua-de-thuong-kante-ngo-tau-ngai-di-hoi-xin-nho-ban-muon-ho-cup-vang-de-song-ao.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/qua-de-thuong-kante-ngo-tau-ngai-di-hoi-xin-nho-ban-muon-ho-cup-vang-de-song-ao-421-191369.html\">Qu\u00e1 d\u1ec5 th\u01b0\u01a1ng! Kante ng\u1ed1 t\u00e0u ng\u1ea1i \u0111i h\u1ecfi xin, nh\u1edd b\u1ea1n m\u01b0\u1ee3n h\u1ed9 c\u00fap v\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1ed1ng \u1ea3o</span><br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a Chelsea ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p tr\u00ean h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1555","checkdouble":"191868"},{"date":"01:47 24/07","title":"T\u00e2n binh Real Madrid h\u1ea1 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/5/24/tan-binh-real-madrid-ha-muc-tieu-vo-dich-champions-league.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd trong ph\u1ea7n \u0111i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u00ean chuy\u00ean trang Bongda24h s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 24/7. \r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o s\u1ebd c\u1ea3n b\u01b0\u1edbc Man City \u1edf m\u00f9a sau?<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Leroy Sane \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00e1 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd, khi cho r\u1eb1ng Chelsea s\u1ebd l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e1ng g\u1eddm trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c cho r\u1eb1ng, The Blues \u0111\u00e3 \u0111em v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc c\u00f9ng l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng \u0111\u1eb9p m\u1eaft. &ldquo;\u0110\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i, h\u00e3y nh\u00ecn c\u00e1ch Napoli thi \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 xem&rdquo; &ndash; Sane cho bi\u1ebft.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 24/7 Ai l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Man City h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 247 Ai l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Man City h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/28/Diem-tin-bong-da-sang-247-Ai-la-doi-thu-lon-nhat-cua-Man-City-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24/7: Sane \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao Chelsea</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi kh\u00f3 Barca<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi CLB T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u01b0a ra l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb th\u1ee9 3 tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 55 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho Willian b\u1ecb t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u1eb7ng h\u1ecfi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 65 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Tuy nhi\u00ean, b\u00e1o ch\u00ed Anh cho bi\u1ebft Chelsea s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb n\u00e0o d\u01b0\u1edbi&hellip; 70 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Ho\u1eb7c ch\u1ecbu chi ra s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3, ho\u1eb7c Barcelona s\u1ebd th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i v\u1edbi m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>M.U \u0111\u1eb7t gi\u00e1 kh\u1ee7ng cho Martial<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Man United \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh, v\u00e0 c\u0169ng t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng, m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb Mourinho treo gi\u00e1. Theo \u0111\u00f3, Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t mu\u1ed1n thu v\u1ec1 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1995, c\u00f9ng \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n ch\u1ec9 b\u00e1n anh b\u00ean ngo\u00e0i Premier League. Bayern v\u00e0 Juve l\u00e0 2 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 ch\u1eef k\u00fd t\u00e0i n\u0103ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb mua s\u1eafm ho\u1ea3ng lo\u1ea1n</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb \u0111em v\u1ec1 Pepe Reina, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n k\u1ef3 c\u1ef1u n\u0103m nay 35 tu\u1ed5i v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 9 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. \u0110\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd, Reina l\u00e0 tr\u00f2 c\u0169 c\u1ee7a HLV Sarri t\u1ea1i Napoli, nh\u01b0ng anh m\u1edbi chuy\u1ec3n sang AC Milan ngay m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y d\u01b0\u1edbi d\u1ea1ng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ef1 do. N\u1ebfu th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 r\u1ea5t h\u00e0i h\u01b0\u1edbc c\u1ee7a The Blues, c\u00f2n nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u1edf Milan b\u1ed7ng d\u01b0ng c\u00f3 9 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 24/7\" title=\"thu mon Pepe Reina toi Milan\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/12/thu-mon-pepe-reina-toi-milan-kiem-tra-y-te.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24/7: Pepe Reina m\u1edbi t\u1edbi Milan v\u00e0 \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Chelsea h\u1ecfi mua</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Karius tr\u00e1ch c\u1ee9 Liverpool v\u00ec mua ng\u01b0\u1eddi<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">The Kop m\u1edbi k\u00edch n\u1ed5 bom t\u1ea5n Alisson tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 67 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 Loris Karius. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, anh \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecf ra kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu khi CLB kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1o tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u1edbi m\u00ecnh v\u00e0 \u0111em v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n m\u1edbi. \u0110\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi, Karius c\u0169ng th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn anh kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft nh\u1eefng g\u00ec m\u00ecnh \u0111ang l\u00e0m l\u00e0 \u0111\u00fang hay sai, sau v\u00f4 v\u00e0n nh\u1eefng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch t\u1eeb sau tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft Champions League.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p &ndash; TTVN</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1554","checkdouble":"191869"},{"date":"01:26 24/07","title":"Mbappe x\u00fai gi\u1ee5c Kante b\u1ecf Chelsea sang PSG","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/23/mbappe-xui-giuc-kante-bo-chelsea-sang-psg.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed3ng Kylian Mbappe ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch PSG nh\u1edd c\u1eady l\u00f4i k\u00e9o \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng N\u2019Golo Kante tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 Ph\u00e1p trong su\u1ed1t chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch World Cup 2018.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u0110\u00f3ng g\u00f3p vai tr\u00f2 t\u1ed1i quan tr\u1ecdng gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u0103ng quang ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi v\u1edbi c\u00fap v\u00e0ng th\u1ee9 hai trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed, t\u00e0i n\u0103ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p c\u1ee7a N\u2019Golo Kante m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa khi\u1ebfn c\u00e1c \u00f4ng l\u1edbn Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u ph\u1ea3i th\u00e8m kh\u00e1t v\u00e0 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m s\u1edf h\u1eefu b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a anh.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">C\u00f3 l\u1ebd nghi\u00eam t\u00fac h\u01a1n c\u1ea3 ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea1i gia Paris Saint-Germain, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed nh\u01b0 theo ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Kylian Mbappe, m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao kh\u00e1c c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00f3i s\u00e1ng r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1 tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga, gi\u1edbi ch\u1ee7 \u1ea2 R\u1eadp \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1edd c\u1eady anh ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u00f4i k\u00e9o \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn \u201cC\u00f4ng vi\u00ean c\u00e1c Ho\u00e0ng t\u1eed\u201d trong su\u1ed1t chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch World Cup 2018.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mbappe x\u00fai gi\u1ee5c Kante b\u1ecf Chelsea sang PSG h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Mbappe x\u00fai gi\u1ee5c Kante b\u1ecf Chelsea sang PSG h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/23/mbappe-xui-giuc-kante-bo-chelsea-sang-psg.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mbappe x\u00fai gi\u1ee5c Kante b\u1ecf Chelsea sang PSG</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed3ng tu\u1ed5i teen ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u: \u201c\u0110\u00fang l\u00e0 ng\u00e0i ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 l\u1eddi v\u1edbi t\u00f4i v\u00e0 t\u00f4i c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 chuy\u1ec3n n\u00f3 \u0111\u1ebfn cho N\u2019Golo khi anh em g\u1eb7p nhau \u1edf World Cup trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n qu\u1ed1c gia.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cTuy nhi\u00ean, t\u00f4i c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u v\u1edbi anh \u1ea5y v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec7n n\u00e0y, hi\u1ec3u r\u1eb1ng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai hay chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng ra sao \u0111\u1ebfn phong \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 t\u00e2m l\u00fd thi \u0111\u1ea5u.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cTh\u1ebf l\u00e0 t\u00f4i g\u1eedi qua m\u1ea9u m\u1ea5u gi\u1ea5y \u0111\u00fat t\u00fai N\u2019Golo, hy v\u1ecdng r\u1eb1ng anh \u1ea5y s\u1ebd ph\u00e1t hi\u1ec7n v\u00e0 \u0111em ra \u0111\u1ecdc \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tin nh\u1eafn t\u1eeb PSG. Anh \u1ea5y th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3, v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 ngo\u1ea1i l\u1ec7.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">N\u00f3i v\u1eady th\u00f4i ch\u1ee9 \u0111\u1ec3 cu\u1ed7m Kante ra kh\u1ecfi Chelsea th\u00ec g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 l\u00e0 nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 b\u1ea5t kh\u1ea3 thi \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf \u1edf Stamford Bridge, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t d\u01b0\u1edbi tri\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1i m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a t\u00e2n HLV Maurizio Sarri.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/qua-de-thuong-kante-ngo-tau-ngai-di-hoi-xin-nho-ban-muon-ho-cup-vang-de-song-ao-421-191369.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/16/qua-de-thuong-kante-ngo-tau-ngai-di-hoi-xin-nho-ban-muon-ho-cup-vang-de-song-ao.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/qua-de-thuong-kante-ngo-tau-ngai-di-hoi-xin-nho-ban-muon-ho-cup-vang-de-song-ao-421-191369.html\">Qu\u00e1 d\u1ec5 th\u01b0\u01a1ng! Kante ng\u1ed1 t\u00e0u ng\u1ea1i \u0111i h\u1ecfi xin, nh\u1edd b\u1ea1n m\u01b0\u1ee3n h\u1ed9 c\u00fap v\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1ed1ng \u1ea3o</span><br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a Chelsea ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p tr\u00ean h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong> <o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1553","checkdouble":"191870"},{"date":"00:00 24/07","title":"L\u0110B\u0110 \u0110\u1ee9c ph\u1ea3n ph\u00e1o Ozil sau c\u00e1o bu\u1ed9c ph\u00e2n bi\u1ec7t ch\u1ee7ng t\u1ed9c","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/23/ldbd-duc-phan-phao-ozil-sau-cao-buoc-phan-biet-chung-toc.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>L\u0110B\u0110 \u0110\u1ee9c ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0a ra th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o ph\u1ea3n ph\u00e1o nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch, c\u00e1o bu\u1ed9c ph\u00e2n bi\u1ec7t ch\u1ee7ng t\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb Mesut Ozil, sau khi ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 29 tu\u1ed5i quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh gi\u00e3 t\u1eeb s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf trong n\u1ed7i u\u1ea5t h\u1eadn.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">B\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u00e0 g\u00e2y x\u00f4n xao, b\u00e0ng ho\u00e0ng d\u01b0 lu\u1eadn, Mesut Ozil quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh chia tay \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c khi ch\u1ec9 m\u1edbi \u1edf tu\u1ed5i 29, b\u1ecf l\u1ea1i 9 n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3 x\u1ee9ng danh c\u00f4ng th\u1ea7n v\u1edbi 23 b\u00e0n/92 tr\u1eadn c\u00f9ng ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2014.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ng\u00f4i sao Arsenal b\u1ecb ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch n\u1eb7ng n\u1ec1 h\u01a1n b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 ai sau chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch World Cup 2018 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda c\u1ee7a Mannschaft. Nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n s\u00e2u xa h\u01a1n v\u1eady khi n\u00f3 d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 b\u1eaft ngu\u1ed3n ch\u00ednh g\u1ed1c g\u00e1c nh\u1eadp c\u01b0 t\u1eeb Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3 v\u00e0 khi\u1ebfn anh b\u1ecb c\u00f4 l\u1eadp, gh\u00e9t b\u1ecf hay g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 k\u1ef3 th\u1ecb, ph\u00e2n bi\u1ec7t ch\u1ee7ng t\u1ed9c.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"L\u0110B\u0110 ph\u1ea3n ph\u00e1o c\u00e1o bu\u1ed9c c\u1ee7a Ozil chia tay \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"L\u0110B\u0110 ph\u1ea3n ph\u00e1o c\u00e1o bu\u1ed9c c\u1ee7a Ozil chia tay \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/23/ldbd-duc-phan-phao-ozil-sau-cao-buoc-phan-biet-chung-toc.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Mesut Ozil chia tay \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c v\u00e0 b\u1ecb L\u0110B\u0110 n\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0 ph\u1ea3n ph\u00e1o v\u00ec c\u00e1o bu\u1ed9c ph\u00e2n bi\u1ec7t ch\u1ee7ng t\u1ed9c</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Tuy nhi\u00ean m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, \u0111\u00edch th\u00e2n L\u0110B\u0110 \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng ph\u1ea3n ph\u00e1o v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o d\u00e0i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u0103ng tr\u00ean trang ch\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. N\u1ed9i dung c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c vi\u1ebft nh\u01b0 sau:<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cNh\u1eefng b\u1ee9c h\u00ecnh ch\u1ee5p chung v\u1edbi t\u1ed5ng th\u1ed1ng Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3 Recep Tayyip Erdogan d\u1ea5y l\u00ean nh\u1eefng d\u1ea5u h\u1ecfi lo ng\u1ea1i trong l\u00f2ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i \u0110\u1ee9c. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u0169ng th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn L\u0110B\u0110 \u0110\u1ee9c c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m trong s\u1ef1 v\u1ee5 l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t l\u1ea5y l\u00e0m ti\u1ebfc khi Mesut Ozil c\u00f3 c\u1ea3m nh\u1eadn r\u1eb1ng anh \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u1ea5n n\u1ea1n ph\u00e2n bi\u1ec7t ch\u1ee7ng t\u1ed9c, trong khi Jerome Boateng th\u00ec ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n r\u1ea5t \u1ed5n.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cL\u0110B\u0110 \u0110\u1ee9c s\u1ebd v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac n\u1ebfu Mesut Ozil v\u1eabn l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean trong \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n qu\u1ed1c gia, nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed3i anh \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111i ri\u00eang cho m\u00ecnh. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng anh \u1ea5y v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 v\u00e0 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi nh\u1eefng c\u00e1o bu\u1ed9c v\u00f4 l\u00fd v\u1ec1 m\u00ecnh m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch c\u00f4ng khai.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i xin nh\u1ea5n m\u1ea1nh L\u0110B\u0110 \u0110\u1ee9c kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd c\u00f3 t\u01b0 t\u01b0\u1edfng ph\u00e2n bi\u1ec7t ch\u1ee7ng t\u1ed9c v\u1edbi b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 ai tr\u00ean th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. Th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 t\u00edc c\u1ef1c tham gia h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 c\u00f4ng t\u00e1c nh\u1eadp c\u01b0 cho \u0111\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc trong r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m qua.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/nhan-vat/mesut-\u00f6zil-nan-nhan-dien-hinh-cua-mot-nuoc-duc-chia-re-vi-chinh-sach-nhap-cu-389-191848.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/23/mesut-zil-nan-nhan-dien-hinh-cua-mot-nuoc-duc-chia-re-vi-chinh-sach-nhap-cu.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/nhan-vat/mesut-\u00f6zil-nan-nhan-dien-hinh-cua-mot-nuoc-duc-chia-re-vi-chinh-sach-nhap-cu-389-191848.html\">Mesut \u00d6zil: N\u1ea1n nh\u00e2n \u0111i\u1ec3n h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c chia r\u1ebd v\u00ec ch\u00ednh s\u00e1ch nh\u1eadp c\u01b0</span><br>\r\nSau \u00d6zil h\u00f4m nay, t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai s\u1ebd c\u00f2n bao nhi\u00eau \u00d6zil n\u1eefa? V\u00e0 nh\u1eefng t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u00f3 g\u1ed1c g\u00e1c n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i kh\u00e1c, \u0111ang tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh trong nh\u1eefng H\u1ecdc vi\u1ec7n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0110\u1ee9c, khi...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1552","checkdouble":"191871"},{"date":"06:16 24/07","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 24/7: B\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Man City m\u00f9a sau","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/5/diem-tin-bong-da-sang-247-bat-ngo-voi-doi-thu-lon-nhat-cua-man-city-mua-sau.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd trong ph\u1ea7n \u0111i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u00ean chuy\u00ean trang Bongda24h s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 24/7. \r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o s\u1ebd c\u1ea3n b\u01b0\u1edbc Man City \u1edf m\u00f9a sau?<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Leroy Sane \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00e1 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd, khi cho r\u1eb1ng Chelsea s\u1ebd l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e1ng g\u1eddm trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c cho r\u1eb1ng, The Blues \u0111\u00e3 \u0111em v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc c\u00f9ng l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng \u0111\u1eb9p m\u1eaft. &ldquo;\u0110\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i, h\u00e3y nh\u00ecn c\u00e1ch Napoli thi \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 xem&rdquo; &ndash; Sane cho bi\u1ebft.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 24/7 Ai l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Man City h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 247 Ai l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Man City h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/28/Diem-tin-bong-da-sang-247-Ai-la-doi-thu-lon-nhat-cua-Man-City-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24/7: Sane \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao Chelsea</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi kh\u00f3 Barca<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi CLB T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u01b0a ra l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb th\u1ee9 3 tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 55 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho Willian b\u1ecb t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u1eb7ng h\u1ecfi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 65 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Tuy nhi\u00ean, b\u00e1o ch\u00ed Anh cho bi\u1ebft Chelsea s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb n\u00e0o d\u01b0\u1edbi&hellip; 70 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Ho\u1eb7c ch\u1ecbu chi ra s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3, ho\u1eb7c Barcelona s\u1ebd th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i v\u1edbi m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>M.U \u0111\u1eb7t gi\u00e1 kh\u1ee7ng cho Martial<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Man United \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh, v\u00e0 c\u0169ng t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng, m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb Mourinho treo gi\u00e1. Theo \u0111\u00f3, Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t mu\u1ed1n thu v\u1ec1 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1995, c\u00f9ng \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n ch\u1ec9 b\u00e1n anh b\u00ean ngo\u00e0i Premier League. Bayern v\u00e0 Juve l\u00e0 2 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 ch\u1eef k\u00fd t\u00e0i n\u0103ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb mua s\u1eafm ho\u1ea3ng lo\u1ea1n</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb \u0111em v\u1ec1 Pepe Reina, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n k\u1ef3 c\u1ef1u n\u0103m nay 35 tu\u1ed5i v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 9 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. \u0110\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd, Reina l\u00e0 tr\u00f2 c\u0169 c\u1ee7a HLV Sarri t\u1ea1i Napoli, nh\u01b0ng anh m\u1edbi chuy\u1ec3n sang AC Milan ngay m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y d\u01b0\u1edbi d\u1ea1ng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ef1 do. N\u1ebfu th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 r\u1ea5t h\u00e0i h\u01b0\u1edbc c\u1ee7a The Blues, c\u00f2n nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u1edf Milan b\u1ed7ng d\u01b0ng c\u00f3 9 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 24/7\" title=\"thu mon Pepe Reina toi Milan\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/12/thu-mon-pepe-reina-toi-milan-kiem-tra-y-te.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24/7: Pepe Reina m\u1edbi t\u1edbi Milan v\u00e0 \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Chelsea h\u1ecfi mua</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Karius tr\u00e1ch c\u1ee9 Liverpool v\u00ec mua ng\u01b0\u1eddi<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">The Kop m\u1edbi k\u00edch n\u1ed5 bom t\u1ea5n Alisson tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 67 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 Loris Karius. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, anh \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecf ra kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu khi CLB kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1o tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u1edbi m\u00ecnh v\u00e0 \u0111em v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n m\u1edbi. \u0110\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi, Karius c\u0169ng th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn anh kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft nh\u1eefng g\u00ec m\u00ecnh \u0111ang l\u00e0m l\u00e0 \u0111\u00fang hay sai, sau v\u00f4 v\u00e0n nh\u1eefng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch t\u1eeb sau tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft Champions League.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p &ndash; TTVN</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1551","checkdouble":"191872"},{"date":"06:30 24/07","title":"Rooney c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o M.U v\u1ec1 hi\u1ec3m h\u1ecda kh\u00f4n l\u01b0\u1eddng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/7/6/rooney-canh-bao-mu-ve-hiem-hoa-khon-luong.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Theo r\u1ea5t s\u00e1t \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u0129nh c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 trong phi\u00ean ch\u1ee3 h\u00e8, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Wayne Rooney khuy\u00ean M.U gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n Martial, n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n ph\u1ea3i \u00f4m h\u1eadn.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nMartial tr\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng r\u1eddi M.U<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi gia nh\u1eadp Old Trafford, tuy nhi\u00ean l\u00fac n\u00e0y Martial \u0111ang b\u1ecb c\u1ea7m t\u00f9 b\u1edfi Jose Mourinho. Anh li\u00ean t\u1ee5c ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb trong k\u1ef7 nguy\u00ean c\u1ee7a Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, v\u00e0 tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i ngay m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. Martial c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec kh\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p l\u1ee1 su\u1ea5t l\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n v\u00e0 ng\u1ed3i nh\u00ecn \u0110T qu\u1ed1c gia l\u00ean ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. V\u1ec1 ph\u00eda ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Martial &ndash; \u00f4ng Philippe Lamboley th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn: &ldquo;Sau khi xem x\u00e9t t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng, v\u00e2ng, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Man United.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;C\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh n\u00e0y. M.U kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n Anthony ra \u0111i v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n gia h\u1ea1n v\u1edbi c\u1eadu \u1ea5y. Nh\u01b0ng th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n \u0111\u00e3 di\u1ec5n ra trong 8 th\u00e1ng v\u00e0 h\u1ecd v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a ch\u1ed1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra b\u1edfi h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n bi\u1ebfn Anthony tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Wayne Rooney khuy\u00ean MU gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n Martial b\u1eb1ng m\u1ecdi gi\u00e1 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Wayne Rooney khuy\u00ean MU gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n Martial b\u1eb1ng m\u1ecdi gi\u00e1 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/23/Wayne-Rooney-khuyen-MU-giu-chan-Martial-bang-moi-gia-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Wayne Rooney khuy\u00ean M.U gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n Martial m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh n\u00e0y, Wayne Rooney l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng khuy\u00ean nh\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 \u0111ang ph\u1ea1m ph\u1ea3i sai l\u1ea7m l\u1edbn. Anh cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u00e0i n\u0103ng \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 r\u1ea5t kh\u00f4n ngoan. Theo c\u00e1ch t\u00f4i nh\u00ecn nh\u1eadn, t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 CLB c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng t\u1ed1i \u0111a kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Anthony. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t Premier League.&rdquo;</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 \u0111\u00f4i khi r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u0111\u1ec3 hi\u1ec3u c\u1eadu \u1ea5y v\u1edbi t\u01b0 c\u00e1ch m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7, m\u1ed9t ch\u00e0ng trai tr\u1ebb tu\u1ed5i, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 con ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a Anthony. M\u1ed9t khi b\u1ea1n l\u00e0m quen v\u1edbi c\u1eadu \u1ea5y, b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef cho Anthony \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c vui v\u1ebb, khi \u0111\u00f3 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd b\u1ed9c l\u1ed9 to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh&rdquo; &ndash; Rooney khuy\u00ean M.U gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n Martial.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hi\u1ec7n nay, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Mourinho \u0111\u1eb7t gi\u00e1 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Tuy nhi\u00ean, M.U ch\u1ec9 b\u00e1n Martial cho nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng b\u00ean ngo\u00e0i Premier League.<br>\r\n&nbsp;<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-chi-ban-anthony-martial-neu-172-191841.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/14/mu-chi-ban-anthony-martial-neu.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-chi-ban-anthony-martial-neu-172-191841.html\">MU ch\u1ec9 b\u00e1n Anthony Martial n\u1ebfu...</span><br>\r\nMU b\u00e1n Anthony Martial n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1edd Manchester Evening News \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-dam-phan-chieu-mo-sao-khung-mu-172-191806.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/21/chelsea-dam-phan-chieu-mo-sao-khung-mu.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-dam-phan-chieu-mo-sao-khung-mu-172-191806.html\">Chelsea \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 sao kh\u1ee7ng MU</span><br>\r\nChelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Anthony Martial c\u1ee7a MU thay Eden Hazard, theo t\u1edd The Times The Blues \u0111\u00e3 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee