fi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00e1c, nh\u01b0ng t\u00e2n HLV c\u1ee7a Chelsea, Maurizio Sarri t\u1ef1 tin gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng 2018.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nSarri quy\u1ebft kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n ng\u01b0\u1eddi<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Thibaut Courtois v\u00e0 Eden Hazard \u0111ang nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb c\u1ee7a Real Madrid, trong khi Barca li\u00ean t\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0a ra nh\u1eefng m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 m\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Willian. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u1ee7 qu\u1ea3n Chelsea d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0o h\u1ee9ng v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c b\u00e1n ng\u01b0\u1eddi, b\u1edfi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 3 trong nh\u1eefng tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, t\u00e2n thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng Chelsea &ndash; \u00f4ng Maurizio Sarri cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi t\u1eebng ng\u01b0\u1eddi, m\u1eb7t \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t. T\u00f4i s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng trao \u0111\u1ed5i v\u1edbi h\u1ecd qua \u0111i\u1ec7n tho\u1ea1i. Th\u1eadt vui khi c\u00f3 Courtois, Willian v\u00e0 Hazard trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh, nh\u01b0ng t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o t\u00f4i. V\u00ec v\u1eady, ch\u00fang ta c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i ch\u1edd.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sarri t\u1ef1 tin gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t \u1edf m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Sarri t\u1ef1 tin gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t \u1edf m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/19/Sarri-tu-tin-giu-chan-tru-cot-o-mua-he-nay-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Sarri t\u1ef1 tin gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t Hazard v\u00e0 Courtois</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div><br>\r\n&ldquo;T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m th\u00edch h\u1ee3p s\u1ebd l\u00e0 cu\u1ed1i th\u00e1ng n\u00e0y, khi h\u1ecd tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Cobham \u0111\u1ec3 luy\u1ec7n t\u1eadp. Khi \u0111\u00f3, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0a ra ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t. B\u00e1o ch\u00ed v\u1ebd ra nh\u1eefng c\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n, h\u1ecd mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7, h\u1ecd b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 h\u00e0ng n\u0103m. C\u00f2n t\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng b\u1ed9 ba n\u00e0y s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i, h\u1ecd l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi nh\u01b0 v\u1eady \u1edf Chelsea.&rdquo;</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;T\u00f4i n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi Willian r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y th\u00edch \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng cho Chelsea. V\u00ec v\u1eady, t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i&rdquo; &ndash; Sarri t\u1ef1 tin tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 1-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Perth Glory, thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng The Blues ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c: &ldquo;K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t, nh\u01b0ng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn t\u00f4i h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng. B\u00e2y gi\u1edd, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 12 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tham d\u1ef1 World Cup. V\u00ec v\u1eady \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ebd c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n qua t\u1eebng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sarri t\u1ef1 tin gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t b\u1edfi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng t\u1ea1i n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh, nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 x\u00e1o tr\u1ed9n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u00e2y ra h\u1eadu qu\u1ea3 kh\u00f4n l\u01b0\u1eddng. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft, Chelsea s\u1ebd ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n Inter Milan \u1edf Nice v\u00e0 Arsenal t\u1ea1i Dublin trong gi\u1ea3i ICC, sau \u0111\u00f3 quay tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Anh \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u Man City trong tr\u1eadn Si\u00eau c\u00fap Anh ng\u00e0y 5/8.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/video-tong-hop-perth-glory-01-chelsea-giao-huu-clb-he-2018-326-191854.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/23/video-tong-hop-perth-glory-01-chelsea-giao-huu-clb-he-2018.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/video-tong-hop-perth-glory-01-chelsea-giao-huu-clb-he-2018-326-191854.html\">Video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Perth Glory 0-1 Chelsea (Giao h\u1eefu CLB h\u00e8 2018)</span><br>\r\nT\u1ea1i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean tr\u00ean c\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ecb thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng Chelsea, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n 59 tu\u1ed5i ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia ph\u1ea7n n\u00e0o th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tri\u1ebft l\u00fd t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh song \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/goc-chelsea-gian-nan-vi-thoi-duong-ho-di-hoa-172-191620.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/19/Sarri-tu-tin-giu-chan-tru-cot-o-mua-he-nay-hinh-anh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/goc-chelsea-gian-nan-vi-thoi-duong-ho-di-hoa-172-191620.html\">G\u00f3c Chelsea: Gian nan v\u00ec th\u00f3i &ldquo;d\u01b0\u1ee1ng h\u1ed5 di h\u1ecda&rdquo;</span><br>\r\n\u00cdt ng\u00e0y qua, HLV Sarri \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m v\u00e0o chi\u1ebfc gh\u1ebf n\u00f3ng t\u1ea1i Chelsea. Nh\u01b0ng ch\u01b0a bi\u1ebft s\u1ebd c\u1ea1nh tranh th\u1ebf n\u00e0o cho ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch, tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft Chelsea...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1548","checkdouble":"191875"},{"date":"06:56 24/07","title":"Sao Man City quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf t\u00e0i n\u0103ng v\u1edbi HLV tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/24/sao-man-city-quyet-tam-chung-to-tai-nang-voi-hlv-tuyen-duc.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sau khi b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf kh\u1ecfi chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch World Cup 2018, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Leroy Sane quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c v\u00e0 c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n m\u00f9a n\u00e0y.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nSane mu\u1ed1n ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf Joachim Low \u0111\u00e3 sai<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean g\u00f3p c\u00f4ng l\u1edbn gi\u00fap Man City v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc, Leroy Sane b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 t\u00ean trong danh s\u00e1ch tham d\u1ef1 World Cup v\u00ec \u00fd \u0111\u1ed3 chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt. B\u1ea3n th\u00e2n \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 \u0111\u1ea1i h\u1ed9i th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng khi b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i ngay t\u1eeb v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a Joachim Low, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Man xanh cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u00fa s\u1ed1c l\u1edbn. T\u00f4i r\u1ea5t th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng khi nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o r\u1eddi tuy\u1ec3n, v\u00e0 m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n trong tu\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Pep Guardiola \u0111\u00e3 trao \u0111\u1ed5i v\u1edbi t\u00f4i trong kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian \u1ea5y. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n v\u00e0 c\u00e1ch t\u00f4i suy ngh\u0129. L\u00fac n\u00e0y, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 mu\u1ed1n t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0 h\u01b0\u1edbng v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd h\u01a1n. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd l\u1edbn, b\u1edfi t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1eb9p.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Leroy Sane quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c sau c\u00fa s\u1ed1c World Cup h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Leroy Sane quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c sau c\u00fa s\u1ed1c World Cup h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/24/sane.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Leroy Sane quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div><br>\r\n&ldquo;Nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i, t\u00f4i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ebfn gi\u1edd v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a ngu\u00f4i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u1ed7i \u0111au, nh\u01b0ng ph\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi v\u00e0 t\u00f4i mong ch\u1edd nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n ti\u1ebfp theo. T\u00f4i \u0111ang c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ec3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t. T\u00f4i bi\u1ebft m\u00ecnh v\u1eabn c\u00f2n nhi\u1ec1u thi\u1ebfu s\u00f3t, nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u00f2n ch\u01a1i hay h\u01a1n n\u1eefa&rdquo; - Leroy Sane quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 sinh n\u0103m 1996 c\u0169ng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ec1 cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch m\u00f9a t\u1edbi, anh ch\u1ec9 ra \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t: &ldquo;Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 \u0111em v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t HLV th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng. Phong c\u00e1ch m\u00e0 Napoli tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n khi \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi CLB c\u1ee7a Sarri.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;C\u00f3 th\u1ec3, Chelsea s\u1ebd c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian l\u00e0m quen v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt, nh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u. H\u1ecd l\u00e0 m\u1ed1i \u0111e d\u1ecda l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i trong con \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 danh hi\u1ec7u v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/sane-khong-trach-low-vi-quyet-dinh-o-nha-xem-world-cup-421-191790.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/22/sane-khong-trach-low-vi-quyet-dinh-o-nha-xem-world-cup.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/sane-khong-trach-low-vi-quyet-dinh-o-nha-xem-world-cup-421-191790.html\">Sane kh\u00f4ng tr\u00e1ch Low v\u00ec quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u1edf nh\u00e0 xem World Cup</span><br>\r\nD\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tham d\u1ef1 ng\u00e0y h\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t h\u00e0nh tinh, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i th\u00ea th\u1ea3m, nh\u01b0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Leroy Sane kh\u00f4ng tr\u00e1ch HLV Joachim...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/cong-than-man-city-quyet-tam-dao-tau-khoi-ach-pep-guardiola-172-191855.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/22/cong-than-man-city-quyet-tam-dao-tau-khoi-ach-pep-guardiola.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/cong-than-man-city-quyet-tam-dao-tau-khoi-ach-pep-guardiola-172-191855.html\">C\u00f4ng th\u1ea7n Man City quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea9u kh\u1ecfi \u00e1ch Pep Guardiola</span><br>\r\nTh\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Joe Hart tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 anh tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 ra \u0111i, l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y l\u00e0 m\u00e3i m\u00e3i \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ee9u v\u00e3n s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p cho m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1547","checkdouble":"191876"},{"date":"15:01 23/07","title":"Bayern b\u00e1o gi\u00e1 mua Vidal cho 2 \u0111\u1ea1i gia th\u00e0nh Milan","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/10/5/bayern-bao-gia-mua-vidal-cho-2-dai-gia-thanh-milan.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Bayern mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n Vidal gi\u00e1 30 tri\u1ec7u Euro. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, Inter Milan \u0111\u00e3 ra gi\u00e1 20 tri\u1ec7u cho ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Chile nh\u01b0ng b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0110\u1ee9c t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Inter mua Vidal</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Champions League sau v\u00e0i n\u0103m v\u1eafng b\u00f3ng, Inter Milan quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m c\u1ee7ng c\u1ed1 l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 mang v\u1ec1 Radja Nainggolan v\u1edbi t\u1ed5ng gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb 38 tri\u1ec7u Euro bao g\u1ed3m c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec3 Davide Santon v\u00e0 Nicolo Zaniolo t\u1edbi AS Roma theo chi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u01b0a d\u1eebng l\u1ea1i \u1edf \u0111\u00f3, Inter mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 th\u00eam 2 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng n\u1eefa. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, Nerazzurri \u0111ang \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n s\u1edf h\u1eefu Sime Vrsaljko c\u1ee7a Atletico Madrid v\u00e0 Arturo Vidal c\u1ee7a Bayern Munich.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Bayern mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n Vidal gi\u00e1 30 tri\u1ec7u Euro cho 2 \u0111\u1ea1i gia th\u00e0nh Milan h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Bayern mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n Vidal gi\u00e1 30 tri\u1ec7u Euro cho 2 \u0111\u1ea1i gia th\u00e0nh Milan h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/10/5/bayern-bao-gia-mua-vidal-cho-2-dai-gia-thanh-milan.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Bayern mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n Vidal gi\u00e1 30 tri\u1ec7u Euro</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Vidal gi\u00e1 30 tri\u1ec7u Euro</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nInter t\u1eebng g\u1eedi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 20 tri\u1ec7u Euro t\u1edbi Bayern \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Vidal song \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i. Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, \u201cH\u00f9m x\u00e1m\u201d kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 thi\u1ebfu th\u1ed1n nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1. Nh\u1eefng Thiago Alcantara, Javi Martinez, Leon Goretzka, Sebastian Rudy, Corentin Tolisso v\u00e0 Renato Sanches \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nBayern s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 Vidal ra \u0111i h\u00e8 n\u00e0y song kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch d\u1ec5 d\u00e3i. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Bavaria mu\u1ed1n 30 tri\u1ec7u Euro, nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb c\u1ee7a Inter 10 tri\u1ec7u Euro.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nBayern hi\u1ec3u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ngo\u00e0i Inter, h\u00e0ng x\u00f3m AC Milan c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd c\u0169ng \u0111ang kh\u00e1t ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a Vidal. Cu\u1ed9c c\u1ea1nh tranh c\u1ee7a hai \u0111\u1ea1i gia th\u00e0nh Milan s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ea9y gi\u00e1 c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Chile l\u00ean \u0111\u00fang v\u1edbi ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i c\u1ee7a ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Uli Hoeness c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c c\u1ed9ng s\u1ef1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Serie A tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/lazio-bat-ngo-hoi-mua-alex-iwobi-172-191833.html\">Lazio b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd mu\u1ed1n r\u00fat ru\u1ed9t Arsenal</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/juventus-nham-ban-hop-dong-dat-gia-nhat-lich-su-mu-thay-pjanic-172-191831.html\">Juventus nh\u1eafm b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t l\u1ecbch s\u1eed MU thay Pjanic</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-nang-gia-hoi-mua-sao-khung-juventus-len-53-trieu-bang-172-191762.html\">Chelsea n\u00e2ng gi\u00e1 h\u1ecfi mua sao kh\u1ee7ng Juventus l\u00ean 53 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/jeremie-boga-roi-chelsea-toi-sassuolo-172-191736.html\">T\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb Chelsea \u0111\u1ebfn Serie A ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1546","checkdouble":"191832"},{"date":"14:52 23/07","title":"Lazio b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd mu\u1ed1n \"r\u00fat ru\u1ed9t\" Arsenal","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/26/lazio-bat-ngo-hoi-mua-alex-iwobi.PNG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Lazio mu\u1ed1n mua Alex Iwobi c\u1ee7a Arsenal, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Italia ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 25 tri\u1ec7u euro mua ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nigeria.</h2><h2>Lazio chi 25 tri\u1ec7u euro mua Iwobi</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Alex Iwobi ch\u01a1i kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Arsenal. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nigeria ghi 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 cung c\u1ea5p 5 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o sau 22 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh. N\u1ebfu t\u00ednh tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi m\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn anh ra s\u00e2n t\u1edbi 39 l\u1ea7n.<br>\r\n<div class=\"imagecontainer\" style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td align=\"center\" style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/1/Lazio-muon-mua-Alex-Iwobi-voi-gia-25-trieu-euro-hinh-anh.jpg\" title=\"Lazio mu\u1ed1n mua Alex Iwobi v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 25 tri\u1ec7u euro h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" alt=\"Lazio mu\u1ed1n mua Alex Iwobi v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 25 tri\u1ec7u euro h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Lazio mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Iwobi</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 22 tu\u1ed5i gi\u00fap anh nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m t\u1eeb m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. Lazio mu\u1ed1n mua Alex Iwobi c\u1ee7a Arsenal, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Italia ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 25 tri\u1ec7u euro mua ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nigeria.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Italia v\u1eeba b\u00e1n Felipe Anderson cho West Ham v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 42.5 tri\u1ec7u euro, h\u1ecd \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 thay th\u1ebf. Lazio nh\u1eafm Iwobi c\u1ee7a Arsenal nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nLazio tin r\u1eb1ng s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n m\u00e0 h\u1ecd d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh chi ra c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Arsenal nh\u1ea3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Italia c\u0169ng ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1996 m\u1ed9t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Lazio c\u00f3 Iwobi l\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNgu\u1ed3n tin t\u1eeb Il Messaggero kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Lazio chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Alex Iwobi \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018 l\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3. Theo \u0111\u00f3, HLV Unai Emery kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 qu\u00e1 cao c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 22 tu\u1ed5i, \u00f4ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea9y Iwobi ra \u0111i \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea5y kinh ph\u00ed \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n<div class=\"imagecontainer\" style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td align=\"center\" style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/1/11/Lazio-bat-ngo-muon-rut-ruot-Arsenal-hinh-anh-2.jpg\" title=\"Lazio b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd mu\u1ed1n r\u00fat ru\u1ed9t Arsenal h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" alt=\"Lazio b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd mu\u1ed1n r\u00fat ru\u1ed9t Arsenal h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Lazio c\u00f3 Iwobi l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 cao</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nS\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n m\u00e0 Lazio \u0111\u01b0a ra \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn Arsenal c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng. N\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ecd c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t cao.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nAlex Iwobi v\u1eeba tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i t\u1eadp trung c\u00f9ng Arsenal, ng\u00f4i sao 22 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f9ng Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 l\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng t\u1edbi Singapore tham d\u1ef1 chuy\u1ebfn du \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf H\u00e8 2018.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Iwobi ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t trong chuy\u1ebfn du \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng anh ph\u1ea3i ra \u0111i l\u00e0 c\u1ef1c cao. HLV Emery \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n Iwobi \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Nzonzi t\u1eeb Sevilla.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1545","checkdouble":"191833"},{"date":"15:32 23/07","title":"Sau Mahrez, Man City s\u1eafp c\u00f3 th\u00eam \"bom t\u1ea5n\" 100 tri\u1ec7u euro","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/2/24/sau-mahrez-man-city-sap-co-them-bom-tan-100-trieu-euro.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trong bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp trung m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o V\u0103n To\u00e0n thay \u0111\u1ed5i ki\u1ec3u t\u00f3c c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt gi\u1eefa c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nV\u0103n To\u00e0n nhu\u1ed9m t\u00f3c th\u1eddi trang<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m qua (22/7), c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u h\u1ed9i qu\u00e2n \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho ASIAD 2018. C\u00f9ng v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u1edf HAGL, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o V\u0103n To\u00e0n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t s\u1edbm nh\u1ea5t \u1edf H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo \u0111\u00f3, t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 12 c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ebfn g\u1eb7p g\u1ee1 HLV Park Hang Seo v\u00e0 c\u00f3 bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, bao g\u1ed3m 8 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 HAGL v\u00e0 4 c\u00e1i t\u00ean c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 Minh Tu\u1ea5n, V\u0103n Ho\u00e0ng, T\u1ea5n Sinh v\u00e0 \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh. Nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i v\u00e0 SLNA ch\u01b0a k\u1ecbp h\u1ed9i qu\u00e2n, b\u1edfi h\u1ecd c\u00f2n ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3i qua v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft c\u00fap qu\u1ed1c gia v\u00e0o \u00edt ng\u00e0y t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"V\u0103n To\u00e0n thay \u0111\u1ed5i ki\u1ec3u t\u00f3c n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt\" title=\"V\u0103n To\u00e0n thay \u0111\u1ed5i ki\u1ec3u t\u00f3c\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/23/van-toan-xuat-hien-voi-kieu-dau-dam-chat-son-tung-mtp.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>V\u0103n To\u00e0n thay \u0111\u1ed5i ki\u1ec3u t\u00f3c n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div><br>\r\nTrong s\u1ed1 n\u00e0y, ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng nh\u1eadn ra h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 \u0111\u1ed9t ph\u00e1 c\u1ee7a Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n To\u00e0n &ndash; ng\u00f4i sao thu\u1ed9c bi\u00ean ch\u1ebf HAGL. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, anh \u0111\u00e3 nhu\u1ed9m m\u00e1i t\u00f3c \u0111en c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh th\u00e0nh m\u00e0u kh\u00f3i x\u00e1m, v\u1edbi hy v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd \u0111em l\u1ea1i may m\u1eafn tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn. Cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai v\u1eeba \u0111\u1ec3 thua SLNA 1-3 t\u1ea1i V-League, v\u00e0 V\u0103n To\u00e0n mu\u1ed1n thay t\u00f3c \u0111\u1ed5i v\u1eadn.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u01b0a bi\u1ebft s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i n\u00e0y c\u00f3 \u0111em l\u1ea1i hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 n\u00e0o cho ch\u00e2n s\u00fat g\u1ed1c H\u1ea3i D\u01b0\u01a1ng hay kh\u00f4ng, b\u1edfi b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u00e1i t\u00ean c\u1ee9 \u0111\u1ed5i t\u00f3c&hellip; l\u00e0 x\u1ecbt, ti\u00eau bi\u1ec3u nh\u01b0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Paul Pogba &ndash; m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p nh\u01b0ng qu\u00e1 sa \u0111\u00e0 v\u00e0o h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh b\u00ean ngo\u00e0i s\u00e2n c\u1ecf.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao kh\u00e1c c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf l\u00e0 Paulo Dybala c\u0169ng thay \u0111\u1ed5i m\u00e0u t\u00f3c n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt nh\u01b0 v\u1eady. C\u00f2n v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda V\u0103n To\u00e0n To\u00e0n thay \u0111\u1ed5i ki\u1ec3u t\u00f3c, nhi\u1ec1u C\u0110V cho r\u1eb1ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y mu\u1ed1n h\u1ecdc theo &hellip; S\u01a1n T\u00f9ng M-TP, m\u1ed9t ca s\u0129 r\u1ea5t n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y mai, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd di chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ebfn trung t\u00e2m PVF \u1edf H\u01b0ng Y\u00ean \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/doi-tuyen-viet-nam/nhung-ai-trong-dt-olympic-viet-nam-phai-len-tap-trung-muon-292-191799.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/26/nhung-ai-trong-dt-olympic-viet-nam-phai-len-tap-trung-muon.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/doi-tuyen-viet-nam/nhung-ai-trong-dt-olympic-viet-nam-phai-len-tap-trung-muon-292-191799.html\">Nh\u1eefng ai trong \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam ph\u1ea3i l\u00ean t\u1eadp trung mu\u1ed9n?</span><br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c tr\u00f9ng l\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u, c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ebfn 13 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam ph\u1ea3i l\u00ean t\u1eadp trung mu\u1ed9n trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho ASIAD 2018.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/doi-tuyen-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-so-bi-quay-lung-ngay-truoc-them-asiad-2018-292-191795.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/22/hlv-park-hang-seo-so-bi-quay-lung-ngay-truoc-them-asiad-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/doi-tuyen-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-so-bi-quay-lung-ngay-truoc-them-asiad-2018-292-191795.html\">HLV Park Hang Seo s\u1ee3 b\u1ecb quay l\u01b0ng ngay tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m ASIAD 2018</span><br>\r\nTrong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho ASIAD 2018, HLV Park Hang Seo s\u1ee3 b\u1ecb quay l\u01b0ng n\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p &ndash; TTVN</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1544","checkdouble":"191834"},{"date":"16:04 23/07","title":"Chelsea c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o Real Madrid v\u1ee5 Eden Hazard","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2016/3/15/them-mot-ngoi-sao-dem-hung-tin-toi-cho-chelsea.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Real Madrid \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a Eden Hazard r\u1eddi Chelsea, song The Blues kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u1ecd s\u1ebd quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m gi\u1eef b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9.</h2><h2>Real quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Hazard</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nReal Madrid \u0111ang quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Eden Hazard thay th\u1ebf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed do Ronaldo \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i, ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Perez ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c The Blues nh\u1ea3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<div class=\"imagecontainer\" style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td align=\"center\" style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/31/Khong-de-de-Real-Madrid-dua-Eden-Hazard-roi-Chelsea-hinh-anh.jpg\" title=\"Kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 \u0111\u1ec3 Real Madrid \u0111\u01b0a Eden Hazard r\u1eddi Chelsea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" alt=\"Kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 \u0111\u1ec3 Real Madrid \u0111\u01b0a Eden Hazard r\u1eddi Chelsea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Real Madrid \u0111ang c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng mua Eden Hazard</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo Daily Mail, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/cuc-nong-chelsea-dong-y-ban-hazard-cho-real-voi-so-tien-sieu-khung-172-191665.html\" target=\"_blank\">Real chi 170 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Hazard</span>, h\u1ecd tin r\u1eb1ng s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n n\u00e0y s\u1ebd thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Chelsea b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1991. Ngo\u00e0i ra, Los Blancos c\u00f2n s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u01b0\u01a1ng cao nh\u1ea5t CLB.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ebfn H\u00e8 2020, Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n chia tay s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge sau 6 n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1eadm ch\u00ed Hazard c\u00f2n kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u1ecdi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1u mu\u1ed1n kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Real Madrid, d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1991 \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Bernabeu \u1edf H\u00e8 2018.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea ng\u0103n c\u1ea3n Hazard t\u1edbi Real</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nReal Madrid \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a Eden Hazard r\u1eddi Chelsea, song The Blues kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u1ecd s\u1ebd quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m gi\u1eef b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9.<br>\r\n<div class=\"imagecontainer\" style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td align=\"center\" style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/13/muon-thanh-cong-hlv-sarri-can-phai-ban-eden-hazard.jpg\" title=\"Sarri mu\u1ed1n bi\u1ebfn Hazard th\u00e0nh trung t\u00e2m trong l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Chelsea\" alt=\"Sarri muon bien Hazard thanh trung tam trong loi choi cua Chelsea\" style=\"border: none\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Chelsea mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef Hazard b\u1eb1ng m\u1ecdi gi\u00e1</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo Mirror, Chelsea \u0111ang c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng gi\u1eef c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i b\u1eb1ng m\u1ecdi gi\u00e1, h\u1ecd s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1edbi 400.000 b\u1ea3ng/tu\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1eef anh \u1edf l\u1ea1i. HLV Sarri y\u00eau c\u1ea7u BL\u0110 The Blues gi\u1eef Hazard b\u1eb1ng m\u1ecdi gi\u00e1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nChelsea c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb t\u1eeb ph\u00eda Real Madrid, ngay c\u1ea3 khi Los Blancos ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 170 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u1ecd c\u0169ng ki\u00ean quy\u1ebft kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Hazard v\u1edbi Chelsea c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 2 n\u0103m, n\u1ebfu The Blues ki\u00ean quy\u1ebft kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 h\u1ecd ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ecb Real \u00e9p gi\u00e1 v\u00e0o H\u00e8 n\u0103m t\u1edbi. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo t\u00ednh to\u00e1n t\u1eeb ph\u00eda Mirror, gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Hazard \u1edf H\u00e8 2019 ch\u1ec9 v\u00e0o kho\u1ea3ng 80 \u0111\u1ebfn 100 tri\u1ec7u euro, b\u1edfi \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u00f3 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a anh v\u1edbi The Blues ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 12 th\u00e1ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1543","checkdouble":"191840"},{"date":"16:27 23/07","title":"MU ch\u1ec9 b\u00e1n Anthony Martial n\u1ebfu...","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/14/mu-chi-ban-anthony-martial-neu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>MU b\u00e1n Anthony Martial n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1edd Manchester Evening News \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i.</h2><h2>Chelsea quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m mua Martial</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nReal Madrid \u0111ang l\u00e0m m\u1ecdi c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/chelsea-canh-bao-real-madrid-vu-eden-hazard-172-191840.html\" target=\"_blank\">Eden Hazard r\u1eddi Chelsea</span>, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 c\u0169ng \u0111ang r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n t\u1edbi Bernabeu. D\u00f9 The Blues kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh song kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ecd gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"imagecontainer\" style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td align=\"center\" style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/14/mu-chi-ban-anthony-martial-neu.jpg\" title=\"MU b\u00e1n Anthony Martial n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u 100 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" alt=\"MU b\u00e1n Anthony Martial n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u 100 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Chelsea v\u00e0 nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn quan t\u00e2m Martial</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nSong song v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Hazard k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi Chelsea c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ea9y m\u1ea1nh vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 thay th\u1ebf. Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Anthony Martial c\u1ee7a M.U l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau s\u1ed1 1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c The Blues nh\u1eafm thay c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nHLV Sarri \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Martial, \u00f4ng nh\u1eafm c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Hazard r\u1eddi Stamford Bridge. Chelsea tin r\u1eb1ng v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 kinh nghi\u1ec7m thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1995 s\u1ebd d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp v\u1edbi l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a The Blues.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i Chelsea th\u00ec Bayern Munich, Real Madrid v\u00e0 PSG c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p, nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y c\u0169ng ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1995 r\u1eddi Old Trafford.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>M.U ch\u1ec9 b\u00e1n Martial n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n c\u1ef1c l\u1edbn</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u1eb7c d\u00f9 Anthony Martial tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, song M.U \u0111ang l\u00e0m kh\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y. Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1995 \u1edf l\u1ea1i Old Trafford.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"imagecontainer\" style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td align=\"center\" style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/24/martial-co-tiem-nang-tro-thanh-cau-thu-xuat-sac-nhat-the-gioi.jpg\" title=\"Martial chi\u1ebfm tr\u1ecdn m\u1eb7t b\u00e1o trong l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ra m\u1eaft\" alt=\"Martial chiem tron mat bao trong lan dau ra mat\" style=\"border: none\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>MU ch\u1ec9 b\u00e1n Martial n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u 100 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Martial v\u1edbi Man \u0111\u1ecf ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ebfn H\u00e8 2019, song M.U c\u00f3 quy\u1ec1n k\u00edch ho\u1ea1t \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n t\u1ef1 gia h\u1ea1n th\u00eam 1 n\u0103m. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo Manchester Evening News, n\u1eeda \u0111\u1ecf th\u00e0nh Manchester mu\u1ed1n k\u00edch ho\u1ea1t \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n t\u1ef1 gia h\u1ea1n th\u00eam 1 n\u0103m \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1eef Martial \u1edf l\u1ea1i. Mourinho d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trung phong \u0111\u1ec3 anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n \u1edf m\u00f9a t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1995 ki\u00ean quy\u1ebft ra \u0111i, MU b\u00e1n Anthony Martial n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i.<br>\r\nC\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, ngu\u1ed3n tin t\u1eeb Manchester Evening News kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford mu\u1ed1n thu v\u1ec1 \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 100 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng t\u1eeb c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 <br>\r\nti\u1ec1n r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn v\u00e0 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn Chelsea hay Bayern s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i suy ngh\u0129 r\u1ea5t k\u1ef9 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u00f3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Martial hay kh\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1542","checkdouble":"191841"}]}